data.description: Very well taken care of home on large lot with screened in porch, new metal roof, new septic system, large Garage/ Workshop. Located on the West side of Foley, just south of 98 and East of 65. Close to everything.  Twenty minutes to the beach.  Just added two more rooms and bathroom.  Kitchen has been remodeled with granite counter tops.  Entire house outside and inside has been painted.  New wood burning fireplace insert.  Working AC/heater in Garage with bathroom.  Must see to appreciate!
